'''South Dakota Circuit''' is a permanent [[motor racing]] track in [[Timehri]], behind the [[Cheddi Jagan International Airport]], [[Guyana]]. It is operated by the Guyana Motor Racing & Sports Club. The circuit hosts national circuit racing including the GMR&SC Skyline Mortgage Caribbean Race of Champions and various drag racing events.<ref>http://www.gmrscgy.com/</ref> On May 9, 2008, the [[Stabroek News]] published a letter from a reader that suggested that the circuit lacks adequate washroom facilities.<ref>http://www.stabroeknews.com/letters/the-south-dakota-circuit-lacks-washroom-facilities/</ref>

